{
  "stem": "10162.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So since that reunion in Germany I was telling you about, they erected a museum in this-- on the site of the old [?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dynamit ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobel ?] headquarters, which was a landmark building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it really is a quite remarkable building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was invited for the opening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was also commissioned to make the only sculpture there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is the catalog from that museum, which is called also a documentation and informational center.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this is the catalog with-- with a photo of my sculpture on the cover, which represents slave laborers there, the way they were-- like the two figures are like one.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One is-- one is with a bowed head, humiliated, heavy in-- heavily-- heavy labor carrying the grenade.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the other one is-- is standing-- standing erect looking upward and letting a bird fly off, representing freedom and our hope.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was in 1992, the museum opening on the book--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was in '93-- '93 or '94 even.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's when I-- I recall-- the sculpture was commissioned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was a landmark building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took a long time to-- to build it just so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the-- it wasn't inaugurated until '94.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my professional name is Aniko Veres-Fe, which Aniko Veres is my maiden name and Fe was added because of other things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the January 16, 1995 edition of magazine, which was an Auschwitz memorial edition that I happened open by chance.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I found myself in this picture, which represents us, part of the 1,000 Hungarian girls, on our way from Auschwitz to this German factory.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I happen to be the tall girl right on the crease.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is a homemade photograph of the-- of a maquette-- of the only holocaust memorial that I ever designed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always believe just like I don't think that-- that words can convey-- convey the inexplicable, the-- the-- the human tragedy that was the Holocaust, I feel the same way about the ability of visual arts to do that.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this I see as preferably a larger than life size bronze-- what--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--would call it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's thin slab, like a--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--slab, where the figures, the figure of a family, would be cut out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it's of the void, the void that it represents in the lives, in the hearts of the survivors as well.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is a side view, obviously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other part of the sculpture is that it would have to be on a large bare terrain.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the way the sun moves or reflectors, it always casts a shadow where the figures emerge in light.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I feel simplicity is the strongest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's the only thing that I would hope to one day to execute.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
